title: Verizon's Quarterly Revenue Rises 5%, Tops Estimates
text:
Published By: Fox Business - Today 
Verizon reported an adjusted 3Q profit of $1.04 per share, topping the estimate for $1.02. Revenue of $33.16 billion, also beat the estimate...
